0C3AEB87.Line13.BD31C: In my shadow, the strong will oppose the might of Hell itself.

4ACA1BC7.Line31.BD31C: The ruination of Sanctuary is imminent. And yet you doubt.

912480F8.Line5.BD31C: I have not come to save, but to empower.

A62F6509.Line15.BD31C: Let the weak fend for themselves.

F438D28C.Line3.8DD12: Only zealots and fools are completely certain, Mother. If we are to be saved, it will be by your hand.
